      • DnxDocumentHelper.EnvironmentSoftware

        public DnxDocumentHelper.EnvironmentSoftware()

      • DnxDocumentHelper.EnvironmentSoftware

        public DnxDocumentHelper.EnvironmentSoftware(java.lang.String softwareName,
                                     java.lang.String softwareVersion,
                                     java.lang.String softwareType,
                                     java.lang.String softwareOtherInformation,
                                     java.lang.String softwareDependancy)
        Creates the EnvironmentSoftware section.
        Parameters:
        softwareName - Manufacturer and title of the software application. (for example, Adobe Photoshop)
        softwareVersion - The version or versions of the software referenced in swName. (for example, >=2.2.0)
        softwareType - Class or category of software. (for example, renderer, operatingSystem)
        softwareOtherInformation - Additional requirements or instructions related to the software referenced in swName.
        softwareDependancy - The name and, if applicable, version of any software component needed by the software referenced in swName in the context of using this object.
